    V4L/DVB (6657): Fix standard selection for PAL/M, PAL/N, PAL/Nc and NTSC
    
    Those standards use 6 MHz firmware.
    
    Signed-off-by: Mauro Carvalho Chehab <mchehab@infradead.org>

